{"tid":1026940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新鮮出爐！英國下議院發表有關假新聞嘅研究報告","createTime":"2019-02-18T12:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T00:17:19.000Z","uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b97bbf0c92504d39f25b88a56bda57175a3507b","tid":1026940,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://houseofcommons.shorthandstories.com/dcms-committee-disinformation-fake-news/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhouseofcommons.shorthandstories.com%2Fdcms-committee-disinformation-fake-news%2Findex.html&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=f57628e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://houseofcommons.shorthandstories.com/dcms-committee-disinformation-fake-news/index.html</a><br />\n【我自己翻譯】<br />\n2017年9月，英國下議院嘅數碼、文化、媒體及體育委員會展開有關不實資訊及「假新聞」嘅調查，報告今日出爐。<br />\n報告呼籲：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">確立法律責任，要求科技公司打擊佢地網站上面嘅有害或非法內容；<br />\n訂立倫理守則，界定何為有害內容；<br />\n由獨立監管部門負責監察科技公司，並賦予該部門法律權力，對違反倫理守則嘅公司採取法律行動。未能打擊有害內容嘅公司將面臨巨額罰款。<br />\n</span><br />\n報告全文：<br />\n網頁版<br />\n<a href=\"https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201719/cmselect/cmcumeds/1791/179102.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201719%2Fcmselect%2Fcmcumeds%2F1791%2F179102.htm&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=7d9979f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201719/cmselect/cmcumeds/1791/179102.htm</a><br />\npdf版<br />\n<a href=\"https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201719/cmselect/cmcumeds/1791/1791.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201719%2Fcmselect%2Fcmcumeds%2F1791%2F1791.pdf&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=6d92a70d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201719/cmselect/cmcumeds/1791/1791.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"5e4af92c6b8b57944d6dad3d1f48e88503e2bf00","tid":1026940,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45420abfc23a25dad82d4406abc549146e965f62","tid":1026940,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07987c515314b3d609e9f8b9da66350e7cbd33f1","tid":1026940,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"其實要啦<br />\n社交媒體底下，國家嘅文化價值同觀點都可以任意俾外國操控同影響<br />\n根本係反智<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但官僚嘅結果就只會加美資科技公司稅<br />\n假消息繼續出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7be5c6166c07d47320e2f6ad9b7312a28cef44c","tid":1026940,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45420abfc23a25dad82d4406abc549146e965f62","tid":1026940,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6bac106012a9d140830fd268ac1bf1f8ef665750","tid":1026940,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f6c82d4f6b928ee5de725d101124f23d90f07026","tid":1026940,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"英國研究喎......"},{"pid":"e4211d43ebf3b6606eee03998bbbde82a4d84eb1","tid":1026940,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"push"}]}